{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/transform-detransform/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"CSS para impacientes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"226b7287-e21a-5b80-91f3-c4e00906b487","excerpt":"Sets a transform on the parent element and de-transforms the child elements, so they are not affected by the transform.\nThis allows for some neat effects such…","html":"<p>Sets a transform on the parent element and de-transforms the child elements, so they are not affected by the transform.\nThis allows for some neat effects such as skewed buttons.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>parent<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Child content<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.parent</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">skewX</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--transform<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.child</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">skewX</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">calc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-1 * <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--transform<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4>Explanation</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--transform: 10deg</code> sets a CSS variable we can later use to prevent duplicate code.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">calc(-1 * var(--transform))</code> on the child element negates the transform from the parent.</li>\n<li>Note: the <code class=\"language-text\">display</code> property of the child element may not be <code class=\"language-text\">inline</code>, otherwise the transform will be ignored (<a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-transforms-1/#terminology\">see also</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Browser support</h4>\n<p><span class=\"snippet__support-note\">⚠️ Requires prefix for full support.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=transforms2d\">https://caniuse.com/#feat=transforms2d</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Transform - Detransform","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/transform-detransform/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/triangle/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Triangle"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/transform-centering/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Transform centering"}}}}}